:INFO
Pre-Launch and Post-Launch Checklist
A complete checklist covering everything to verify before going live and the first actions to take after launch day.

:TASK
[ ] Landing page copy reviewed and proofread
[ ] Stripe payments tested end to end
[ ] Email confirmation flow working
[ ] Error pages and edge cases handled
[ ] Analytics tracking installed
[ ] Support email address set up
[ ] Launch post drafted for Product Hunt
[ ] Announce to email waitlist
[ ] Post in three relevant online communities
[ ] Follow up with every new signup within 24 hours
[ ] Review analytics after 48 hours
[ ] Schedule week two retrospective

:NOTE
Write your post-launch thank-you email before launch day. You will not have time to write it well in the chaos of a live launch. Prepare it in advance and send it within two hours of going live.